ObjectStates.Name: PiecePack_Suns
ObjectStates.Description: This tool uses a script to name and give descriptions to cards. Generated with wstools.
ObjectStates.XmlUI:
<Defaults>
    <Panel class="Window" width="400" height="175" color="#FFFFFF40" outline="#404040" />
    <Panel class="TopBar" height="30" rectAlignment="UpperCenter" color="#191970" />
    <Text class="WindowTitle" fontSize="18" height="20" fontStyle="Bold" rectAlignment="UpperCenter" color="#FFFFFF" />
    <Button class="topButtons" width="20" height="20" rectAlignment="UpperRight" color="#eeeeee" />
</Defaults>

<Panel class="Window" id="deckGeneratorWindow" allowDragging="True" returnToOriginalPositionWhenReleased="false" rectAlignment="MiddleRight">
    <Panel class="TopBar" id="TopBar">
        <Text class="WindowTitle" offsetXY="0 -5">Generate Deck</Text>
        <!--
        <Button id="minimizeButton"
            class="topButtons"
            textColor="#000000"
            text="_"
            offsetXY="-25 -5"
            onClick="minimize"/>
        -->
        <Button id="closeButton"
                class="topButtons"
                color="#990000"
                textColor="#FFFFFF"
                text="X"
                offsetXY="-5 -5"
                onClick="close" />
    </Panel>
    <InputField id="deckImageText"
                onValueChanged="setDeckImage"
                offsetXY="180 5"
                preferredWidth="250"
                rectAlignment="MiddleRight"
                placeholder="Paste Image Here...">
    </InputField>
    <InputField id="charaSleevesText"
                onValueChanged="setCharacterSleeves"
                offsetXY="180 -30"
                preferredWidth="250"
                rectAlignment="MiddleRight"
                placeholder="https://i.imgur.com/fRYj5tS.jpg">
    </InputField>

    <VerticalLayout>
        <GridLayout cellSize="190 25"
                    spacing="10 10"
                    rectAlignment="MiddleCenter">
            <Text></Text>
            <Text></Text>

            <Text>Deck Name</Text>
            <Text id="deckNameText" />

            <Text>Deck Image URL</Text>
            <Text></Text>

            <Text>Deck Sleeves URL</Text>
            <Text></Text>
        </GridLayout>
        <Button id="generateButton" onClick="generateDeckViaUI">Generate</Button>
    </VerticalLayout>
</Panel>
